    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and has been maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom-quality shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with all systems functioning exactly as they did when it first left the factory. It comes with a complete service history and has always been garaged, making it a rare find for a discerning buyer who wants the best example available.",
      "price": 49000.0,
