    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished example of automotive engineering, maintained to a high standard of excellence. This vehicle offers a harmonious balance of performance and sophistication, having undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure its continued mechanical integrity. The exterior retains its luster, while the interior provides a refined environment for the discerning driver. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a well-preserved asset that promises both reliability and prestige.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
